<opener><lb/>Viro <abbr>Exc.</abbr> atque <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Petro Antonio Michelotti</rs>
<lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person"><abbr>N. B.</abbr></rs></opener>
<p><lb/>Gratias Tibi ago maximas pro transmisso felici nuntio de facta
         <lb/>confirmatione electionis me<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ad <rs type="organisation">Cathedram Mathematicam</rs>,
         <lb/>quam post liberationem <rs key="place_WEI-korfua" type="place">Insul<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Corcyr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> et profligatos Turcas,
         <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#klammerauf">|:</g></orig><reg>(</reg></choice>de qua re et <abbr>Ser.</abbr> <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Rei public<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> et toti Europ<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Christian<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
         <lb/>gratulor<choice><orig><g ref="#klammerzu">:|</g></orig><reg>)</reg></choice> brevi secuturam esse sperabam. Quamvis autem nesciam
         <lb/>an copia Decreti <rs type="organisation">Senatus</rs>, quam <rs key="B_1716-09-25_991170515017105501" type="letter">epistol<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> Tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ad <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruum</rs>
<lb/>meum dat<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> adjecisti, instar vocationis solennis esse debeat,
         <lb/>quia tamen <choice><abbr>Illmor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></abbr><expan>Illustrissimorum</expan></choice> et <abbr>Exc.</abbr> <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089586175 pers_DE-588-121843858 pers_DE-588-1253768439" type="persons">Reformatorum</rs> voluntatem
         <pb facs="1038353" n="140v"/>
<lb/>esse scribis, ut citissime in vestras oras me conferam et quam<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>primum provinciam mihi concreditam aggrediar, parebo Illo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rum voluntati, quocirca Deo volente post 15<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> dies iter aggrediar.
         <lb/>Faxit ille su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>us Deus, ut hoc meum propositum et conatus mei
         <lb/>in sui honorem cedant et spem <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place"><abbr>Ser.</abbr> <abbr>Republ.</abbr></rs> et <abbr>Exc.</abbr> <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089586175 pers_DE-588-121843858 pers_DE-588-1253768439" type="persons">Reforma<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>toribus</rs> de me conceptam impleant! C<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terum maxime me Tibi
         <lb/>obstrictum habes, pro su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>a diligentia, quam impendisti ad negoti<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
         <lb/>hoc ad felicem exitum deducendum, et quam etiamnum impendere
         <lb/>dignaris ad necessaria mihi <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavii</rs> paranda. Puto non necesse
         <lb/>esse domum conduci, quia donec linguam et morem vestratium
         <lb/>aliquatenus addiscam, mallem uti hospitio et mensa amici cujusdam,
         <lb/>pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cipue gratum mihi foret, si apud aliquem ex Professoribus
         <lb/>co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>orari liceret. <rs type="biblio">Lectiones</rs> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patrui</rs> mei de sublimiori Mathesi, c<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>te<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>raque scripta, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> quidem conquirere potero, afferre non negligam.
         </p><lb/><closer>Det Deus ut Te salvum et incolumen amplectar. Vale igitur et
         <lb/>fave. <dateline><date when="1716-10-10">10. Oct. 1716</date>.</dateline></closer>
</div></body></text></TEI>